Honours[edit]



As a player[edit]

Individual


PFA Third Division Team of the Year: 1976–77
PFA Second Division Team of the Year: 1978–79 & 1981–82


Hednesford Town


Staffordshire Senior Cup winner: 1970[4]


with Brighton & Hove Albion


Football League Third Division runner-up: 1976–77[4]
Football League Second Division runner-up: 1978–79[4]


with Luton Town


Football League Second Division champion: 1981–82[4]


 

As a manager[edit]

Individual


Football League Second Division Manager of the Month: March 2001,[22] February 2002,[30] August 2003[48]
Football League Two Manager of the Month: February 2005[67]


with Hull City


Football League Third Division 3rd place promotion winner: 1984–85[4]


with Port Vale


Football League Trophy winner: 2001[104]
Staffordshire Senior Cup winner: 2001




