Non-Profit Boards ▾




Member, Board of Directors

                    Current                  


Goodwill Industries of Orange County, California

                    Goodwill Industries of Orange County, California provides people with disabilities and other barriers the opportunity to achieve level of personal and economic independence through employment. Its programs assists individuals with work and social abilities, cultural and language skills and to help them succeed at home, at school and in the workplace. The company was founded in 1924 and is headquartered in Santa Ana, CA.                  





